`Graphics::drawIndexedTriangleList(0,minVtx,numVtx,startIndex,primCount)` → `Graphics.cpp:3315` → 
`drawPartialIndexedTriangleList` → `DrawIndexed(primCount*3, startIndex, baseIndex=0)`). Verified: 
write-byte == IA-read-byte for every lock (no offset divergence).
