.planning\research\CONSULT-27-E-codex.out:1650:> ### How GAP-6 was actually fixed (the multi-stream 
theory was WRONG)
.planning\research\CONSULT-27-E-codex.out:1655:>    NOT require activating multi-stream â€” 
single-stream per-key remap sufficed, so the
.planning\research\CONSULT-27-E-codex.out:1656:>    `SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive` 
