whether their VB carries a color stream. Compare the D3D9 asset VS (it DOES read vertex 
color/COLOR0). **A RenderDoc capture of one black building draw (gl05 vs gl11) would show the VB 
color stream + VS input sig in one look** — get RenderDoc back for this.
