.planning\research\CONSULT-30-SONNET-lateral.out:41:  stream 1: m_staticStream (color + 2D UVs)
.planning\research\CONSULT-30-SONNET-lateral.out:44:the single-stream path copies systemStream 
(which holds ALL components) into dynamicStream via
.planning\research\CONSULT-30-SONNET-lateral.out:45:`outIt.copy(m_systemStream->beginReadOnly(), 
