off, position-at-0 still correct (fits "position clean"); Cursor 30 only checked the CURRENT format, 
not a stale cached layout — WORTH CHECKING the input-layout cache key/stride at garment draws. 
**(Rank 7) `getRingBuffer()` NULL-fallback to MAIN ring** if a garment binds before its first lock 
(m_ringBuffer==nullptr) — a risk introduced by the 16MB skin-ring split; reverting the skin ring 
removes it. Full: `CONSULT-30-SONNET-lateral.out`.
